ُظْلَمُونَ فَتِيلًۭا","translation":"[but] one Day We shall summon all human beings [and judge them] according to the conscious disposition which governed their deeds [in life]: whereupon they whose record shall be placed in their right hand -it is they who will read their record [with happiness]. Yet none shall be wronged by as much as a hair's breadth:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2100.mp3","surahId":17,"words":[{"id":60016,"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","translation":"যেদিন","audioUrl":"wbw/017_071_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60017,"position":2,"arabic":"نَدْعُوا۟","translation":"আমরা ডাকবো","audioUrl":"wbw/017_071_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60018,"position":3,"arabic":"كُلَّ","translation":"প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/017_071_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60019,"position":4,"arabic":"أُنَاسٍۭ","translation":"মানবদলকে","audioUrl":"wbw/017_071_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60020,"position":5,"arabic":"بِإِمَـٰمِهِمْ ۖ","translation":"সহ তাদের নেতা","audioUrl":"wbw/017_071_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60022,"position":6,"arabic":"فَمَنْ","translation":"অতঃপর যাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/017_071_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60023,"position":7,"arabic":"أُوتِىَ","translation":"দেয়া হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/017_071_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60024,"position":8,"arabic":"كِتَـٰبَهُۥ","translation":"কর্মফল তার","audioUrl":"wbw/017_071_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60025,"position":9,"arabic":"بِيَمِينِهِۦ","translation":"মধ্যে তার ডানহাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/017_071_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60026,"position":10,"arabic":"فَأُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ","translation":"ঐসব লোক","audioUrl":"wbw/017_071_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60027,"position":11,"arabic":"يَقْرَءُونَ","translation":"তারা পড়বে","audioUrl":"wbw/017_071_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60028,"position":12,"arabic":"كِتَـٰبَهُمْ","translation":"কর্মফল তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/017_071_013.mp3","charTypeN